PrecisOrder accepting a "DESIGNATION" duly approved by the NORTHLANDS BAND OF INDIANS whereby the band conditionally surrenders some 2.27 hectares (5.60 acres) of land situate on LAC BROCHET INDIAN RESERVE No. 197A, in the Province of Manitoba, for a term of twenty (20) years, so that they can be leased to The North West Company Inc. for commercial purposes.
